event.name: Managing College Life
event.description: Managing your life in college can be hard, especially in the first years. For most people, transitioning from high school to college is going to a new place with no friends and it’s filled with lots of work. It’s not an easy process for most, so attend this informative event to learn more about how to be a successful college student! Ask any questions you might have and receive useful insight from someone successful who’s been in your shoes before.
